# Skype Chatbot

This is a modular chatbot for Skype.

## Skype Mac OSX Note:

Skype4Py segfaults when attaching with 64-bit Python (I guess Skype is still 32bit)
In the meantime, use this defaults setting to eliminate the error:

defaults write com.apple.versioner.python Prefer-32-Bit -bool yes


### Easy Install Dependencies:

sudo easy_install Skype4Py
sudo easy_install SQLAlchemy
sudo easy_install argparse
sudo easy_install httplib2
sudo easy_install whoosh
sudo easy_install pattern
sudo easy_install pywapi


### Yelp Dependency Install

svn checkout http://yelp-python-client.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ yelp-python-client
cd yelp-python-client
python setup.py install


## How to run:

1. Install dependencies
2. Launch Skype
3. cd into the directory hosting chatbot
4. run the chatbot with: python chatbot.py
5. The skypebot automatically assumes your name, so have somebody send you a message like:   [your name] hello

